body:
Um... now that i have your attention let me explain what has been happening to me for the past few months before you send a Truck full of hate in the form of a ding dong up my wham ham chute....

Over the past few years I have been experiencing game crashes and random disconnects dating back from October of 2015 the game has been working fine before I have been playing since Zed came out... And from 2015 and on that mark it has been a bumpy road for me... {{item:3070}} {{champion:32}}  {{item:3070}} 

Now fast forward to today, I was about to play my game it's loading everyone is at 100% i'm also 100% I'm still at the loading screen like for 10 mins and come to find out that the game already ended... I'm here like okay and i'm still at the loading screen we get to the results screen my name is on the Red so I have to play 5 games and have to wait for 20 mins... This is a unjust punishment for a person that want's to play a really good game. I thought I was loading still. So the question lies, we banning people over a game crashing??? tell me now so I can uninstall and take my business to Valve....


